overview: Three hacker friends earn a living by hacking social networks and gadgets, collecting compromising materials and blackmail. Exploring the life of the owner of an art gallery, the mysterious Alika Eliseeva, they find themselves involved in a terrible game. Now they must stop the terrible sweepstakes and save the loved ones who got into it, but their own lives may become the price.
title: Darknet. The Mousetrap
